{
  "stem": "27340.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And since the company that my grandfather founded was called S.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Mendelsson and Son, it was going to be simple for me ultimately to also become an S.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Mendelsson to take over the company.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But that was not to happen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was, of course, not to happen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The company, like all other organizations, Jewish organizations, were totally destroyed, confiscated.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so I in fact left Germany and was never in a position to take up that position.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went to school.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think I must have been 5 or 6 when I started school.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I went to a local school, a primary school, elementary-- I suppose we call it a primary school, junior school.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there, we had about 30 children in the class, and amongst them were 6 or 7 Jewish children.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And one of the teachers was a particularly-- I wouldn't like to say pro-Jewish, but certainly was very tolerant towards Jewish children.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I remember an incidence when he had announced that he was going to show in the geography lesson-- he was going to show some slides.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In those days, we're talking about 1933, '34, '35, that was still quite something fairly advanced and unusual.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we were all looking forward to this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there was one German girl who sat behind me and said, oh, goody. goody.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That means that when you're going to show the slides on the announced date, the Jewish kids won't see it because of it will be Yom Kippur and they won't be here.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And when he heard this, he changed the date of the showing of the slides.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it was very, very sad, but four weeks later or so, he was removed from his position and I do not know what has happened to him.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
